This project implements ZIP signing and verification using the APK Signature
Scheme v2 block format.

The implementation was written with reference to the Android Open Source
Project documentation and the AOSP apksig reference implementation:

  https://source.android.com/docs/security/features/apksigning/v2
  https://android.googlesource.com/platform/tools/apksig/

Android Open Source Project materials are licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0, unless otherwise noted by the Android Open Source Project.

No AOSP source files are vendored in this repository.
